Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment‚Äôs mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi‚Äôs love?

snippet.title: CANDY | COLORFUL TUTTI FRUTTI Candy with Ice Cream | Papaya Harvesting and Cooking in Village
snippet.description:
Today, we cook a colorful Tutti Frutti recipe using farm-fresh raw papaya. Tutti Frutti is a sweet candy made from papaya, which is also used for baking. We harvest fresh papaya from the Papaya farm to make the colorful Tutti Frutti candy.

Finally, We eat this Tutti Frutti with Ice Cream! Yummy!

snippet.title: Matka Teaser | Varun Tej | Karuna Kumar | Meenakshi Chowdary | Nora Fatehi | GV Prakash Kumar
snippet.description:
Get ready for a high-octane experience with the action-packed teaser of  #Matka! Featuring Varun Tej, Meenakshi Chowdary, and Nora Fatehi, with a powerful soundtrack by GV Prakash Kumar, directed by Karuna Kumar. A thrilling treat awaits!

Stay updated with the latest videos, Subscribe on the link - http://bit.ly/adityamusic
Click here to share on Facebook- https://bit.ly/3v3iHeg  

#MATKA is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun tej in the Lead Role, Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

The story which takes place between 1958-1982 is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years. 

Cast: #VarunTej, #MeenakshiChowdary, #NoraFatehi, Naveen Chandra, Kannada Kishore, Ajay Ghosh, Mime Gopi, Roopalakshmi, Vijayrama Raju, Jagadeesh, Raj Thirandas.

Get ready for a high-octane experience with the action-packed teaser of  #Matka! Featuring Varun Tej, Meenakshi Chowdary, and Nora Fatehi, with a powerful soundtrack by GV Prakash Kumar, directed by Karuna Kumar. A thrilling treat awaits!

Stay updated with the latest videos, Subscribe on the link - http://bit.ly/adityamusic
Click here to share on Facebook- https://bit.ly/3v3iHeg  

#MATKA is an upcoming Periodical Film starring Mega Prince Varun tej in the Lead Role, Written and Directed by Karuna Kumar. It also co stars Meenakshi Chowdary, Nora Fatehi, Naveen Chandra and others. Music by GV Prakash Kumar, Cinematography by A Kishor Kumar and Proudly Produced on a massive scale by Dr. Vijender Reddy Teegala and Rajani Talluri under Vyra Entertainments in Association with SRT Entertainments

The story which takes place between 1958-1982 is based on a real incident that shook the entire nation and the story is set in the backdrop of Vizag. The story spans 24 years.

Title: Durga Chalisa
Singer: Anuradha Paudwal

Lyrics: Traditional

Lyrics:
Jai Jai Durge Maa
Jai Jai Ambe Maa
Jai Jai Durge Maa
Jai Jai Ambe Maa

Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni
Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni
Nirakar Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari

Shashi Lalaat Mukh Maha Vishala
Netra Lal Bhrikouti Vikarala
Roop Maatu Ko Adhik Suhave
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Paave
Tum Sansar Shakti Ley Keena
Palan Hetu Anna Dhan Deena
Annapoorna Hui Jag Paala
Tumhi Aadi Sundari Bala

Pralayakal Sab Nashaan Haari
Tum Gouri Shiv Shankar Pyari
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaavein
Brahma Vishnu Tumhein Nit Dhyaave
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara
De Subuddhi Rishi Munina Ubara
Dhara Roop Narsimha Ko Amba
Pragat Bhayi Phaad Kar Khamba

Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo
Hiranyaykush Ko Swarg Pathayo
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahin
Shree Narayan Anga Samahin

Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilaasa
Daya Sindhu Deejey Mann Aasa
Hingalaja Mein Tumhi Bhawani
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani

Matangi Dhoomawati Mata
Bhuvaneshwari Bagala Sukhdata
Shree Bhairav Tara Jag Tarini
Chhinna Bhala Bhava Dukh Nivarini
Kehari Vahan Sohe Bhawani
Laangur Veer Chalat Agavani
Kar Mein Khappar Khadaga Virajay
Jako Dekh Kaal Darr Bhajey

Sohe Astra Aur Trishula
Jate Uthata Shatru Hiya Shoola

Nagkoti Mein Toumhi Virajat
Tihoun Lok Mein Danka Baajat
Shumbh Nishumbh Daanav Tum Maare
Rakta Beej Shankhana Sanghaare
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulaani

Roop Karaal Kali Ka Dhara
Sena Sahita Tum Tihin Samhara
Pidh Pari Santana Par Jab Jab
Bhayi Sahay Maat Tum Tab Tab
Amarpuri Auro Sab Lokaa
Tab Mahima Sab Rahey Ashoka
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tumhein Sada Poojey Nar Nari

Prem Bhakti Se Jo Jas Gaave
Dukh Daridra Nikat Nahin Aave
Dhyave Jo Nar Man Layi
Janma Maran Tako Chhouti Jaayi
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukaari
Yog Nahi Bina Shakti Tumhari
Shankar Acharaj Tap Kinho
Kaamaru Krodh Jeet Sab Leenho

Nishdin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko
Kaahu Kaal Nahin Sumiro Tumko
Shakti Roop Ko Maram Na Paayo
Shakti Gayi Tab Mann Pachitayo
Sharnagat Huyi Kiriti Bakhai
Jai Jai Jai Jagadambe Bhawani

Bhayi Prasanna Aadi Jagadamba
Dayi Shakti Nahin Keen Vilamba

Maukon Maatu Kashta Ati Ghero
Tum Bin Kaun Hare Dukh Mero
Asha Trishna Nipat Satave
Ripu Murakh Mohi Ati Darpave
Shatru Nash Keejai Maharani
Soumiron Ikchit Tumhein Bhawani
Karo Kripa Hey Maatu Dayala
Riddhi Siddhi Dey Karahou Nihaala

Jab Lagi Jiyoun Daya Phal Paun
Tumharo Jas Mein Sada Sunaun
Durga Chalisa Jo Koi Gaavey
Sab Sukh Bhog Parampad Paave

Devidas Sharan Neej Jaani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani

Sharanagat Raksha Kare
Bhakt Rahe Nishank
Me Aaya Teri Sharan Mein
Matu Leejiye Ank

Today our Josh Talks speaker is Sanjay Sir, founder of Disha Online Classes.

In a small village, where new hopes arose with the first ray of the sun every morning, there was a child named Sanjay. Sanjay was born in a labourer family, where financial constraints limited his dreams.
Sanjay's childhood was full of hardships. He used to work as a labourer r to help his family. One day, when he was returning after cutting grass, some people of the village were making fun of him. But Sanjay made these taunts his inspiration. He decided that he would do something big with his hard work and dedication.
Due to poverty at home, Sanjay could not go out and study. But he did not give up. He studied on his own and made every effort to increase his knowledge. He would learn from books, search for information on the Internet and work hard day and night to make his dreams come true.
Sanjay started Disha Online Classes on YouTube. His hard work and dedication made him a viral teacher. His videos inspired millions of students and made them understand the importance of education.

Today our Josh Talks speaker is Sanjay Sir, founder of Disha Online Classes.

In a small village, where new hopes arose with the first ray of the sun every morning, there was a child named Sanjay. Sanjay was born in a labourer family, where financial constraints limited his dreams.
Sanjay's childhood was full of hardships. He used to work as a labourer r to help his family. One day, when he was returning after cutting grass, some people of the village were making fun of him. But Sanjay made these taunts his inspiration. He decided that he would do something big with his hard work and dedication.
Due to poverty at home, Sanjay could not go out and study. But he did not give up. He studied on his own and made every effort to increase his knowledge. He would learn from books, search for information on the Internet and work hard day and night to make his dreams come true.
Sanjay started Disha Online Classes on YouTube. His hard work and dedication made him a viral teacher. His videos inspired millions of students and made them understand the importance of education.

This journey of Sanjay Sir is not only inspirational but also shows that through education and technology we can make our dreams come true.

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 73 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 3rd October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she‚Äôs not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

1. India Capitals Squad for LLC 2024: Ian Bell, Dwayne Smith, Ashley Nurse, Dhawal Kulkarni, Dhruv Rawal, Barinder Sran, Ravi Bopara, Parvinder Awana, Naman Ojha,Chris Mpofu, Iqbal Abdulla, Kirk Edwarks, Pankaj Singh, Pawan Suyal, Rahul Sharma, Gnaneswara Rao, Faiz Fazal, Colin De Grandhomme, Bharat Chipli, Ben Dunk.

Sreesanth, Ishwar Pandey, Debarata Das, Manan Sharma, John Mooney,Yashpal Singh, Asghar Afghan, Jerome Taylor, Lendl Simmons, Liam Plunkett, Morne Van Wyk, Samar Quadri, Seekkuge Prasanna, Shannon Gabriel, Kamau Leverock.

3. Konark Suryas Odisha Squad for LLC 2024: Irfan Pathan, Ross Taylor, Yusuf Pathan, Ambati Rayadu, Pravin Tambe, Kevon Cooper, Jesse Ryder, Kevin O'Brien, Fidel Edwards,Richard Levi, Vinay Kumar, KP Appanna, Ben Laughlin, Dilshan Munaweera, Diwesh Pathania, Navin Stewart, Rajesh Bishnoi, Shabaz Nadeem. 

4. Manipal Tigers Squad for LLC 2024: Harbhajan Singh, Thisara Perera, Solomon Mire, Manoj Tiwary, Pragyan Ojha, Upul Tharanga, Angelo Perera, Imran Khan, Saurabh Tiwary,Sheldon Cottrel, Abu Nechim, Amit Verma, Amitoze Singh, Anureeth Singh, Asela Gunaratne, Dan Christian, Praveen Gupta, Rahul Shukla.

5. Southern Superstars Squad for LLC 2024: Dinesh Karthik, Parthiv Patel, Kedar Jadhav, Abdur Razzak, Hamilton Masakadza, Martin Guptill, Suranga Lakmal, Elton Chigumbura,Chathuranga De Silva, Chirag Gandhi, Hamid Hassan, Jeevan Mendis, Jesal Karia, Monu Kumar, Pawan Negi, Robin Bist, Shreevats Goswami, Suboth Bhati. 

6. Toyam Hyderabad Squad for LLC 2024: Suresh Raina, Peter Trego, Isuru Udana, Stuart Binny, Gurkeerat Singh Mann, Sudeep Tyagi, Monty Panesar, Shivakant Shukla, Shadab Jakati,Ricardo Powell, Abid Nabi, Chadwich Walton, Rikke Clarke, Jaskaran Malhotra, George Worker, Yogesh Nagar, Samiullah Shinwari, Nuwan Pradeep, Bipul Sharma.


‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶‚Ä¶.Legends League Cricket

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills,
engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport.¬†
At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness,
providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters.¬†

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by
Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas,
Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation‚Äôs cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing
powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants.¬†

Current Teams:
Manipal Tigers, Toyam Hyderabad, Southern Superstars, India Capitals, Konark Suryas Odisha, Gujarat Greats
Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the
world come once again to compete and inspire.¬†The new season of Legends League Cricket will be happening in India from 20th September to 16th October. Legends League Cricket
reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let‚Äôs celebrate the spirit of cricket together!

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills,
engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport.¬†
At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness,
providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters.¬†

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by
Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas,
Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation‚Äôs cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing
powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants.¬†

Current Teams:
Manipal Tigers, Toyam Hyderabad, Southern Superstars, India Capitals, Konark Suryas Odisha, Gujarat Greats
Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the
world come once again to compete and inspire.¬†The new season of Legends League Cricket will be happening in India from 20th September to 16th October. Legends League Cricket
reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let‚Äôs celebrate the spirit of cricket together!
